{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "e0a1f3b0-0000-4000-8000-c0a1f3b0e040",
    "name": "log-ingest-service (P4.3 enrich)",
    "description": "Smoke contract for log-ingest-service. P4.0 introduced POST /api/v1/ingest/batch returning 202. P4.1 lit up the persistence path with server-computed event_id + UNIQUE (tenant_id, event_id) cold-path dedupe + JSONB roundtrip. P4.2 layered Redis SETNX hot-path dedupe on the Idempotency-Key header, server-side PiiMasker (second layer after the agent), and publishes cortex.ingest.dedupe.hits + cortex.ingest.mask.applied Micrometer counters to /actuator/prometheus. P4.3 adds server-side enrichment: X-Request-Id / X-Correlation-Id propagation onto labels.trace_id, JWT tid claim resolution (precedence over X-Tenant-Id), label normalization (lowercase keys, trim values, last-write-wins), and a geo_country stub label that is always present (ADR-0024).",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
